cat << EOF
tgif is a vector-based drawing tool, with the additional benefit of
being sort of a web-browser. That is, you can fetch drawings from a
web server with it, and you can make objects in your picture into
hotlinks to other parts of the drawing, or to other drawings
accessible via HTTP.
EOF
